---
// Projects.astro
---

<section id="projects" class="projects-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">DESARROLLO DE VIDEOJUEGOS</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">El ala de desarrollo e incubación de videojuegos retro de Ogres Games.</p>
    
    <div class="simple-construction-box pixel-border">
      <div class="status-badge arcade-font">
        <span class="status-dot"></span>
        ESTADO: SECCIÓN EN PLANIFICACIÓN
      </div>
      <p class="construction-text">
        Actualmente estamos enfocados al 100% en expandir y enriquecer nuestra comunidad gamer y en nuestros servidores dedicados (Minecraft Pokémon, etc.). 
        El desarrollo y lanzamiento de videojuegos independientes propios se encuentra bajo estudio y diseño de conceptos para el futuro.
      </p>
      <div class="construction-footer">
        <a href="#servers" class="pixel-button arcade-font">VER SERVIDORES</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .projects-section {
    padding: 100px 0;
    border-top: 3px solid #141026;
    background-color: rgba(7, 5, 14, 0.5);
  }

  .section-desc {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-top: -30px;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .simple-construction-box {
    max-width: 650px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: #0d0a1c;
    border-color: var(--neon-purple);
    padding: 40px 30px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(188, 19, 254, 0.25), inset 0 0 10px rgba(188, 19, 254, 0.1);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .simple-construction-box::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--neon-purple), var(--neon-pink), var(--neon-purple));
  }

  .status-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--neon-pink);
    text-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--neon-pink-glow);
    background-color: rgba(255, 0, 127, 0.08);
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border: 2px solid var(--neon-pink);
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 0, 127, 0.15);
  }

  .status-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--neon-pink);
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--neon-pink);
    animation: pulse-dot 1.2s infinite alternate;
  }

  @keyframes pulse-dot {
    0% { opacity: 0.4; }
    100% { opacity: 1; }
  }

  .construction-text {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    max-width: 520px;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }

  .construction-footer {
    margin-top: 20px;
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .construction-footer .pixel-button {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    border-color: var(--neon-cyan);
    color: var(--neon-cyan);
    background: transparent;
    padding: 12px 30px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--neon-cyan-glow);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .construction-footer .pixel-button:hover {
    background-color: var(--neon-cyan) !important;
    color: #07050e !important;
    box-shadow: 0 0 18px var(--neon-cyan) !important;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 576px) {
    .simple-construction-box {
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }
    
    .status-badge {
      font-size: 0.55rem;
      padding: 8px 14px;
    }
  }
</style>
